{"tid":1808404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(回帶)藏有過百支槍械 5000發子彈 判囚18個月","createTime":"2020-01-02T10:42:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T11:08:10.000Z","uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5c62c61ef208f8552473619623152c8123c77f3b","tid":1808404,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:42:28.000Z","msg":"槍械：118支槍械，包括0.22口徑湯臣「挑戰者」來福槍、M14自動步槍、五六式步槍等十多支真槍，其餘有氣槍，模型槍<br />\n<br />\n子彈：5,000發，包括300發是可射穿裝甲車穿甲彈<br />\n<br />\n炮彈：30毫米口徑迫擊炮彈殼，催淚手榴彈等<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/news/art/20110417/15174379\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20110417%2F15174379&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPgwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=a564806e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20110417%2F15174379&h=bd8455e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/news/art/20110417/15174379</a><br />\n<br />\n被指是「隱世槍王」的退休一級懲教主任梁國熾，因為是槍械發燒友故獲發槍牌，惟他去年在家抹槍時不慎走火受傷，從而揭發他家中另有非法「軍火庫」。被告早前承認一項無牌管有火器彈藥罪，法官昨於高院判刑時指，槍牌條例在九七年已修改，即使持有槍牌也不得在家管有槍彈；而被告雖持槍牌逾廿多年，卻漠視有關條例及家中有年幼孫兒，在家中無牌藏槍且不上鎖，罪行嚴重，判囚不可免。但考慮被告個人背景，最終只判他入獄十八個月。<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20121027/00176_100.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20121027%2F00176_100.html&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPgwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=b683d7e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20121027/00176_100.html</a>"},{"pid":"a48ce1829ca2c7978d9c58d22dcb71b2ab3b3ef6","tid":1808404,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:43:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"337b64b749133051a79c498de90a1489d6e90b1b","tid":1808404,"uid":274161,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:44:09.000Z","msg":"收埋兩支汽油彈判一年<br />\n收埋個軍火庫都只係判多半年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40fb9e263c6173aa84454bc5e39b13a326266e83","tid":1808404,"uid":37869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"337b64b749133051a79c498de90a1489d6e90b1b","tid":1808404,"uid":274161,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:44:09.000Z","msg":"收埋兩支汽油彈判一年<br />\n收埋個軍火庫都只係判多半年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:45:33.000Z","msg":"知法犯法 罪減一等<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c1badecca1793cee360762e0911aac98b943314","tid":1808404,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40fb9e263c6173aa84454bc5e39b13a326266e83","tid":1808404,"uid":37869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"337b64b749133051a79c498de90a1489d6e90b1b","tid":1808404,"uid":274161,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:44:09.000Z","msg":"收埋兩支汽油彈判一年<br />\n收埋個軍火庫都只係判多半年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:45:33.000Z","msg":"知法犯法 罪減一等<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:47:06.000Z","msg":"有委任証等於有免死金牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b3d664878a089275608643ce6d7b5be394e8234","tid":1808404,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:52:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d90f77b9a5eea96a22cd107a4f2ffb363a578d40","tid":1808404,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T10:56:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f298352242b3ef19b0a634b1ff36828e1395e75","tid":1808404,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T11:04:41.000Z","msg":"前懲教主任「公屋槍王」梁國熾因在家中抹槍時走火射傷大腿，被揭發無牌藏槍和子彈，去年被判囚18個月。上訴庭認同判刑過輕，昨天接受律政司申請，將刑期增加至30個月。<br />\n<br />\n65歲的梁國熾原只可合法持有14支槍，惟其家中藏槍彈量超過規定，去年承認無牌管有火器及彈藥罪，原定於今年8月刑滿出獄。他昨天坐在犯人欄內，面容憔悴，聽到其律師提及他喪女一事時，流淚低泣。<br />\n<br />\n律政司一方指，根據案例，無牌藏槍彈而不涉及非法用途，起刑點介乎6年至12年。本案被告，無牌藏7支槍及逾4,000發子彈，數量之多，起刑點應為8年。即使被告遭遇喪女之痛，但不能解釋他為何要大量藏有槍彈。<br />\n<br />\n上訴庭副庭長楊振權指本案涉及大量槍彈，認為起刑點應為5年監禁，因被告認罪減刑三分一，及考慮其求情因素再減刑10個月，最後將刑期定為30個月。<br />\n<br />\n另控方指截至上月底，本港共有137名持牌人士，可在家中藏有槍械，當中涉及327支槍，但持牌人士須將彈藥存放在槍械庫，現時只有一人獲准在家中藏彈藥。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20130321/18202100\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20130321%2F18202100&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPgwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=6bef237b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20130321%2F18202100&h=321741cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20130321/18202100</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢單嘢原審判18個月都轟動一時 DOJ就刑期上訴 <br />\n 上訴庭裁定量刑起點應該係8年 扣認罪2/3同接納求情理由最終加刑到30個月"},{"pid":"1df20035f63d0c46bed46af99b72bd133dc1f85b","tid":1808404,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f298352242b3ef19b0a634b1ff36828e1395e75","tid":1808404,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T11:04:41.000Z","msg":"前懲教主任「公屋槍王」梁國熾因在家中抹槍時走火射傷大腿，被揭發無牌藏槍和子彈，去年被判囚18個月。上訴庭認同判刑過輕，昨天接受律政司申請，將刑期增加至30個月。<br />\n<br />\n65歲的梁國熾原只可合法持有14支槍，惟其家中藏槍彈量超過規定，去年承認無牌管有火器及彈藥罪，原定於今年8月刑滿出獄。他昨天坐在犯人欄內，面容憔悴，聽到其律師提及他喪女一事時，流淚低泣。<br />\n<br />\n律政司一方指，根據案例，無牌藏槍彈而不涉及非法用途，起刑點介乎6年至12年。本案被告，無牌藏7支槍及逾4,000發子彈，數量之多，起刑點應為8年。即使被告遭遇喪女之痛，但不能解釋他為何要大量藏有槍彈。<br />\n<br />\n上訴庭副庭長楊振權指本案涉及大量槍彈，認為起刑點應為5年監禁，因被告認罪減刑三分一，及考慮其求情因素再減刑10個月，最後將刑期定為30個月。<br />\n<br />\n另控方指截至上月底，本港共有137名持牌人士，可在家中藏有槍械，當中涉及327支槍，但持牌人士須將彈藥存放在槍械庫，現時只有一人獲准在家中藏彈藥。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20130321/18202100\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20130321%2F18202100&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPgwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=6bef237b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20130321%2F18202100&h=321741cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20130321/18202100</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢單嘢原審判18個月都轟動一時 DOJ就刑期上訴 <br />\n 上訴庭裁定量刑起點應該係8年 扣認罪2/3同接納求情理由最終加刑到30個月"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T11:06:51.000Z","msg":"原來係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d09eff700f7063335b426aef75213b257afb8191","tid":1808404,"uid":133159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T11:08:10.000Z","msg":"持有槍牌 但係抹槍不慎走火<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}